Canonical website:
  https://www.lysator.liu.se/liboop/

Canonical download:
  https://ftp.lysator.liu.se/pub/liboop/liboop-1.0.1.tar.gz

-------------------------------------------

Build instructions:
  1. unpack liboop-1.0.1-X-src.tar.xz
  2. if you use setup to install this src package,
     it will be unpacked under /usr/src automatically
        % cd /usr/src
        % cygport ./liboop-1.0.1-X.cygport all

This will create:
  /usr/src/liboop-1.0.1-X-src.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop4-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop-devel-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop-glib2_0-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop-glib2-devel-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop-rl0-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop-rl-devel-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop-tcl0-1.0.1-X.tar.xz
  /usr/src/liboop-tcl-devel-1.0.1-X.tar.xz

-------------------------------------------

